---

<ProductLayout {title} heading="Kitchens" {description} {images} {faqs}>
  <div class="text-xl">
    <p>Bespoke kitchens made to fit your home, whether modern, traditional, or farmhouse. Every cupboard, drawer, and island is built from quality timber and thought out to make the most of your space. Give us a call on <strong>01228 512303</strong> to talk through your layout.</p>

    <h3 class="mt-12 mb-4">What We Offer</h3>
    <ul class="feature-list mb-2">
      <li>Modern, traditional, and farmhouse kitchens</li>
      <li>Custom kitchen islands for functionality and style</li>
      <li>Optimised storage solutions for plates, pans, and appliances</li>
      <li>High-quality bespoke cabinetry tailored to your home</li>
      <li>Designs that maximise space while maintaining aesthetic appeal</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</ProductLayout>
